{"type": "article", "id": 7747, "title": "Buster LED 灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-25T07:36:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060523460885Kv4BLnoHOby7Ga.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tBuster + Punch 推出的这款灯名为 Buster，其特点是采用了最先进的 LED 技术以节省电力。预计这款灯的电量消耗只有传统灯泡的二十分之一，但预期寿命可达一万个小时，是传统灯泡的 7 倍多。设计灵感是爱迪生的丝灯灯泡。灯泡内部放置了一个树脂导光管，玻璃外壳有温暖的金色、烟灰色与水晶色可以选择。目前售价为 39.99 英镑，<a href=\"http://busterandpunch.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052346066ZkxtEiTwfAamPqs.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75794621\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523460637GFv2ofVhsLIBOn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.69804401\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234606pr0sAObCyZBJe5ul.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.68948655\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234607TwD6fcizFSY1LsaE.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70415648\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234607fl7wLr6SeqUtOAgy.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70415648\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !